data.description: This gorgeous home offers many perks including manufacturer warranties through 2030 for the HVAC, foundation, structure of the home; and through 2045 for the roof shingles. This open concept 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 1,796 sq ft. home offers a completely open view from the kitchen into dining and living area. Relax on the covered back porch in this tranquil neighborhood, The HOA offers a pool, splashpad, playground, and picnic areas to enjoy a relaxing family outing away from home all conveniently nearby or explore the outdoors at the Lake Houston Wilderness Park and Nature Center all within a short drive only minutes away. No need to look any further! Don't miss out on our current promotion, call today to schedule a showing to your new home!
